{"tid":1944004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我好似開始係迷失中搵返自己","createTime":"2020-03-26T06:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T13:18:00.000Z","uid":92132,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"511e56e70a9366f5ac5869685e22f09517b1aa15","tid":1944004,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"開始搵返一個樂觀 鐘意成日笑 比歡樂其他人既自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2319457b282f14ae94c96bff0aa883d535c82cb9","tid":1944004,"uid":319607,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"恭喜你變返一個On9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fd8a3238f098c2ee83c99c1ef15565a5d4d905","tid":1944004,"uid":92132,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"2319457b282f14ae94c96bff0aa883d535c82cb9","tid":1944004,"uid":319607,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"恭喜你變返一個On9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"雖然我係一個ON9仔 但至少我係一個會努力既ON9仔<br />\n最近諗通左D野<br />\nON9係我性格 帶比你地歡樂我會開心 <br />\nON9同識照顧人係可以共存<br />\n無謂令自己變成一個懶係認真嚴肅成熟既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626bfa9006eb37687bc26a7819e4905f1f9e40b4","tid":1944004,"uid":277980,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:28:36.000Z","msg":"加油呀 係一個好好嘅開始<br />\n希望你以後都咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會有咁嘅轉變嘅？"},{"pid":"9d3666b898e1fbed04bb7f6c5821b051c73df5c5","tid":1944004,"uid":92132,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"626bfa9006eb37687bc26a7819e4905f1f9e40b4","tid":1944004,"uid":277980,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:28:36.000Z","msg":"加油呀 係一個好好嘅開始<br />\n希望你以後都咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會有咁嘅轉變嘅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"你真係問起我<br />\n可能呢幾個星期 <br />\n思考得太多人生哲理<br />\n睇太多人地既愛情故事<br />\n反思呢兩年感情既一點一滴<br />\n嘗試逼自己做一個嚴肅認真成熟既男人<br />\n但慢慢我覺得唔似自己<br />\n就想一直搵個平衡點<br />\n點樣可以做自己同時又可以識得照顧人又會為目標努力進步<br />\n岩岩聽聽下歌就諗通左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7da1e399cbd6b81272b57b96309743cdb00be2","tid":1944004,"uid":41859,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:39:13.000Z","msg":"過2日又頹返"},{"pid":"08d099639c1832c2012674916fbc5dd9462edd7d","tid":1944004,"uid":92334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4b7da1e399cbd6b81272b57b96309743cdb00be2","tid":1944004,"uid":41859,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:39:13.000Z","msg":"過2日又頹返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250ce683bdc442159c3b1e08ff15deecb46ffa69","tid":1944004,"uid":92132,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"4b7da1e399cbd6b81272b57b96309743cdb00be2","tid":1944004,"uid":41859,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:39:13.000Z","msg":"過2日又頹返"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"暫時呢一刻 我都唔會比自己頹落去既<br />\n至少我有PLANING每日應該要做D咩<br />\n或者係我想改變D咩<br />\n就好似<br />\n要減肥&gt;我隔日要做HIIT/每日控制自己糖奶吸收量/要食多菜烚蛋<br />\n要練好英文FOR將來考牌&gt;每日用半個鐘至一個鐘搵篇英文文章讀下/每粒字都要查清楚練讀音<br />\n要提升自己果行既知識&gt;每日上網睇人打既BLOG/睇返文章<br />\n要減壓&gt;每日玩SWITCH半個鐘至一個鐘左右/唱歌<br />\n學煮野食&gt;假日搵我媽學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我份人鐘意係EX面前做ON9野<br />\n但我同自己講 我唔會再犯同一個錯 (就係不懂分吋 係唔岩TIMING做ON9野)<br />\n呢方面真係表現得好唔成熟 好似只係得自己開心 忽略左人地覺唔覺我開心 (大家千其唔好學)<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個星期令我學識一句野<br />\n接受自己既唔完美 先可以令自己進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣又要行商務搵書 每日都好BUSY <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97